social_posts.post_text:
🧘🏻‍♀️🗺️⛰️🎦
After (I really don’t know how many miles we hike but my Apple Watch said I walk 9,550 steps) gallons of water and a sandwich, we made it ❤️ and it worth it.

📍 Fossil Creek.
You need a permit and a parking 🅿️ I paid $12 for ours.
It was really sunny ☀️ and hot but the water was perfectly cold. 
- Print your parking permit in advance 
- Bring lots of water 💦 (cold and keep some extra water back in your car in a small cooler so you have water to drink once you’re done)
- Water shoes are a lifesaver.
- Bring lunch 🥪 
- Don’t forget to bring your trash with you

Do you know you can drink MUSHROOMS 🍄 coffee and reducing inflammation??

I LOVE COFFEE ❤️ but we all know coffee can make you feel bloated and anxious. So when I found out about coffee mushrooms, i did my research and found out about all the benefits. Obviously it doesn’t taste like coffee but it’s really close and taste good. Just like coffee you can make it hot, cold, brew etc. 
✨use your creativity.

For mine I used:
.1 Tbsp or Ryze (mushroom coffee)
.8-10oz cold water
.non-dairy creamer Almondmilk & oat milk caramel macchiato STARBUCKS (whatever you want) I don’t like it super sweet so I added a splash.
.cinnamon & pumpkin pie spice
.ice 🧊

Exited to play around with different flavors since now on, feel lighter and no regrets. 

If you have a different  recipe DM it to me or just leave it in the comments, I want to try new things with mushroom coffee. Possibilities are endless.

Cabaña 3. Zeuhary San Marcos, Baja California Mexico📍

Entire cabin for 2 guest
1 bedroom 
1 bath 
1 small kitchen and room service till 8PM
Pet friendly ❤️
1 free bottle of wine 🍷 
1 jacuzzi 

They are 4 cabins in total connected but private at the same time. We never saw our neighbors to be honest.
 
Find yourself in the middle of nowhere in San Marcos. Peaceful place, surrounded by vineyards 🍇.

You can find restaurants around you, Airbnbs and more vineyards. Sunsets are insane beautiful 🌅

Prices can vary depending on the day. We stayed Saturday/Sunday and paid $242 plus tax and cleaning fees. 

Check in at 3 PM and checkout at 12 PM. Hostess replies quick so that’s a plus.

One tip: bring your own speaker, the audio for the movie doesn’t work and read the same review here on IG. Other then that I would recommend this cute gateway 💯
